name: Princess Castle Runner 3D
description:
Teenager princess in amazing dress is running home from the ball. She was preparing for this party for a few days – beauty salon, stylist, shopping etc., and as a result, the party was really great! There was a lot of music, food, drinks and dancing, of course, but now it’s time to go home – prince and parents are worrying. You have to hurry up to get home in time! Princess Castle Runner 3D – party is over, let’s go home!

Tap arrow buttons to turn. Don’t be slow, else princess will fall into the abyss and never meet her family again. Your goal is to reach castle and get home. Good luck!

Princess Castle Runner 3D game features:
- Addictive runner;
- Beautiful cute princess;
- Different levels;
- Falling platforms – you have to be fast;
- Perfect game to train reaction and attention;
- Cool graphic and smooth animation;
- Fairy tale game.

Help our cinderella princess get home as fast as possible! Princess Castle Runner 3D – prince is waiting!
